		<description><![CDATA[Good on you mate, for sharing your great wealth of knowledge. I have also been afflicted with a debilitating condition that has kept me from doing nearly as much playing out as I once did. I&#039;ve been a musician for 37 years. Nearly five years ago I was playing regularly with three bands and doing some session work. One night in the middle of the first song of our set, I started missing changes and forgetting what key we played every song in.

After some labwork and a few doctors visits I was diagnosed with acute encephalopathy onset from NASH Disease. Now I check your lessons weekly to retrain myself as I have forgotten what nearly 30 years of pro playing had taught me. I cannot thank you enough for providing these lessons!!]]></description>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Good on you mate, for sharing your great wealth of knowledge. I have also been afflicted with a debilitating condition that has kept me from doing nearly as much playing out as I once did. I&#8217;ve been a musician for 37 years. Nearly five years ago I was playing regularly with three bands and doing some session work. One night in the middle of the first song of our set, I started missing changes and forgetting what key we played every song in.</p>
<p>After some labwork and a few doctors visits I was diagnosed with acute encephalopathy onset from NASH Disease. Now I check your lessons weekly to retrain myself as I have forgotten what nearly 30 years of pro playing had taught me. I cannot thank you enough for providing these lessons!!</p>
