I&#039;m really glad to have stumbled across your videos!  I have decent chops, but my theory has always been rather weak, so my horizons are expanding thanks to you. 

A lot of people have chimed in with health advice.  At the risk of being pedantic, I will throw my 2 cents in as well.  I got turned on to a water system, that alkalizes the water as it purifies it.  Mine is a Kangen/Enagic machine, but there are other manufacturers out there.  It&#039;s better than bottled water, RO water, tap water, or anything else, and it allows your body to heal itself better and faster.  

After being on that water for a couple months, I could bend over and touch my toes, something I couldn&#039;t do in the 10 years prior.  Give it a shot, it&#039;s something you can do along with any other treatment you do, and the worst that can happen is nothing.]]></description>
